  TO REPLACE WITH YOUR GOOGLE AI STUDIO UI:
  
  1. Copy the HTML from Google AI Studio
  2. Paste it in place of the <section> element above
  3. If you have CSS, add it in a <style> block below
  4. If you have JavaScript, add it in a <script> block below
  5. Update the Props interface if you need different props
-->

